column2: SELECT    m.id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,    n.objid, n.distance,   o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,   str(o.psfMag_g,#,#) as g,str(o.psfMagErr_g,#,#) as err_g, into MYDB.out2_tdi_cal from MyDB.input_tdi_cal AS m    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
